      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum mechanics model form is well-established for metallic implant constructs under quasi-static loading. Material nonlinearity included for post-yield behavior. Model form selection justified by prior literature and comparison to three independent FEA implementations (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes). Required level 3 reflects medium model risk."
