      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Sample size and multi-laboratory design provide sufficient statistical basis for validation comparison. Required level 3 warranted by medium model risk level and the need to capture inter-laboratory variability in bench test results."
