    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the COU is explicitly scoped to static compression-bending only and does not extend to fatigue or other loading modes. All quantitative acceptance bounds for output comparison are satisfied across three independent QoIs and two laboratories.",
